snippet.title: Prison Architect: Undead - Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
Wishlist Now: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2154010/Prison_Architect__Undead/

Undead brings a whole new scenario to Prison Architect: one where the only objective is to survive! With this new, spooky, expansion wardens will have to fight off the undead attacks to save their inmates and free the prison from an unprecedented catastrophe. 

Paradox on YouTube:
